<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Then I acknowledged my sin to you,</para>

<para style="q1">and I no longer hid my iniquity.</para>

<para style="q1">I said, "I will confess my transgressions to Yahweh,"</para>

<para style="q1">and you forgave the guilt of my sin.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Because of this, all who are godly should pray to you at a time of great distress.</para>

<para style="q1">Then when the surging waters overflow, they will not reach those people.</para>
